<div class="panel-inner">
  <h2 class="panel-title">About Me</h2>

  <div class="about-layout">
    <div class="about-body">
      <p>
        I'm Ofer — a geospatial scientist with a strong focus on urban mobility and data-driven approaches
        to understanding cities. I work at the intersection of spatial analysis, machine learning, and
        practical problem-solving, turning complex datasets into insights that can shape infrastructure
        decisions and public policy.
      </p>
      <p>
        I hold a Master's degree in Geography from Tel Aviv University, where my thesis examined the
        impact of cycling infrastructure on riding behaviour using a dataset of over one million shared
        e-scooter rides. That work deepened my conviction that rigorous spatial analysis — applied to
        real movement data — can reveal patterns that genuinely inform how we design and govern urban space.
      </p>
      <p>
        What drives me is the connection between geospatial data, analytical methods, and ML techniques
        applied to urban mobility in a way that is practical — not just academic. I care about producing
        outputs that lead somewhere: to a policy recommendation, an infrastructure change, a clearer
        understanding of how people move through cities.
      </p>
      <p>
        Beyond transportation, I manage GIS systems and Spatial Data Infrastructure (SDI) projects in
        Zanzibar and Ogun State, Nigeria. In these roles I bridge the gap between client business needs
        and open-source GIS solutions — shaping requirements, leading development and technical teams,
        and then supporting knowledge transfer so clients can sustain what we've built together.
      </p>
      <p>
        I don't limit myself to a single domain. I take the knowledge and skills I've built and apply
        them wherever they're useful — and I keep learning along the way.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="about-sidebar">
      <div class="skills-section">
        <h3 class="skills-title">Tech Stack</h3>
        <div class="chips">
          <span class="chip">QGIS</span>
          <span class="chip">ArcGIS</span>
          <span class="chip">PostgreSQL / PostGIS</span>
          <span class="chip">Python</span>
          <span class="chip">Pandas</span>
          <span class="chip">GeoPandas</span>
          <span class="chip">Leaflet</span>
          <span class="chip">NetworkX</span>
          <span class="chip">scikit-learn</span>
          <span class="chip">GeoServer</span>
          <span class="chip">GeoNode</span>
          <span class="chip">GDAL</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <hr class="skills-divider" />

      <div class="skills-section">
        <h3 class="skills-title">Soft Skills</h3>
        <div class="chips">
          <span class="chip chip-soft">Project Management</span>
          <span class="chip chip-soft">Team Leading</span>
          <span class="chip chip-soft">Agile Development Management</span>
          <span class="chip chip-soft">Technical Documentation</span>
          <span class="chip chip-soft">Long-term Planning</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
.about-layout {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 240px;
  gap: 0;
}

.about-body {
  padding-right: 40px;
}
.about-body p {
  font-size: 0.975rem;
  line-height: 1.85;
  color: var(--ct-muted);
  margin-bottom: 20px;
}
.about-body p:last-child {
  margin-bottom: 0;
}

.about-sidebar {
  padding-left: 32px;
  border-left: 2px solid var(--border);
}

.skills-section {
  padding: 4px 0;
}

/* Title indented to align with chip text (chip has 2px border-left + 10px padding) */
.skills-title {
  font-size: 0.7rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--accent);
  margin-bottom: 12px;
  padding-left: 12px;
}

.chips {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 7px;
}

/* Left-accent bar style — text starts flush with title */
.chip {
  display: block;
  font-size: 0.8rem;
  font-weight: 500;
  padding: 3px 0 3px 10px;
  border-left: 2px solid var(--accent);
  background: none;
  border-radius: 0;
  color: var(--ct-muted);
}

.chip-soft {
  border-left-color: transparent;
  padding-left: 10px;
}
.chip-soft::before {
  content: "–";
  margin-right: 7px;
  color: var(--accent);
}

.skills-divider {
  border: none;
  border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  margin: 20px 0;
}

@media (max-width: 760px) {
  .about-layout {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  }
  .about-body {
    padding-right: 0;
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--border);
    padding-bottom: 28px;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }
  .about-sidebar {
    padding-left: 0;
    border-left: none;
  }
}
</style>
